          "id": "Markdown-0c780dd7-4c25-49fe-b8cb-a66454fb1201",
          "text": "To use the Puck platform, you must purchase a usage license.\n\nThe license includes:\n\n- Uncapped usage of the Puck platform recipe\n- Regular platform updates via private NPM registry\n- Technical recipe support\n- Prioritized technical Puck support\n\n## Fees\n\n- **Setup**: $10,000 one-off payment\n- **License (monthly)**: $5,000 / mo\n- **License (annual)**: $50,000 / year ($4,000 / mo)\n\nReduced fees are available via our Early Access Programme.",
